  <div data-section="vendor-audit"><label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="va-02-position" data-section="vendor-audit" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">GSC: average position for target-term pages — anything on page 1?</div></div></label></div>
  <div data-section="vendor-audit"><label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="va-03-trajectory" data-section="vendor-audit" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Is monthly click volume accelerating or flat? (the compound-vs-dud tell)</div></div></label></div>
  <div data-section="vendor-audit"><label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="va-04-promptlist" data-section="vendor-audit" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Get the full LLM prompt-tracking list — check for cherry-picking</div></div></label></div>
  <div data-section="vendor-audit"><label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="va-05-cost" data-section="vendor-audit" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Confirm the monthly fee + itemized breakdown</div></div></label></div>
  <div data-section="vendor-audit"><label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="va-06-ownership" data-section="vendor-audit" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Confirm content + data ownership survives a separation</div></div></label></div>
  <div data-section="vendor-audit"><label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="va-07-opascope" data-section="vendor-audit" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Opascope: signed SOW + last 3 monthly deliverable reports</div></div></label></div>
  <div data-section="vendor-audit"><label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="va-08-7knots" data-section="vendor-audit" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">7 Knots: reconcile what we pay vs. what we actually consume</div></div></label></div>
